Package umontreal.iro.lecuyer.simprocs.dsol

Class Summary
SimProcess Represents a simulation process whose actions method is interpreted by the DSOL interpreter, written by Peter Jacobs (http://www.tbm.tudelft.nl/webstaf/peterja/index.htm).
SSJInterpretationOracle Determines which classes should be interpreted by the DSOL interpreter during process simulation.
